text: Abdelkrim Baadi (born 14 April 1996) is a Moroccan professional footballer who plays as a leftback for HUSA and the Morocco national football team. ==International career== Baadi made his professional debut for the Morocco national football team in a 0-0 tie with Malawi on 22 March 2019, in a 2019 Africa Cup of Nations qualification match. ==References== ==External links== * * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:People from Agadir Category:Moroccan footballers Category:Morocco international footballers Category:Hassania Agadir players Category:Botola players Category:Association football fullbacks Category:2019 Africa Cup of Nations players
